  "keyFeatures": [
    "Recursive, event-driven scan engine that discovers data exponentially across modules",
    "100+ built-in modules for subdomain enumeration, web scanning, OSINT, and more",
    "Preset system for combining modules into reusable scan profiles (subdomain-enum, web-thorough, kitchen-sink, etc.)",
    "Python API for programmatic scanner control (sync and async)",
    "Native output to Neo4j, Postgres, MySQL, SQLite, Elasticsearch, CSV, JSON, Slack, Discord, Teams, and more",
    "NLP-powered subdomain mutation brute-forcing",
    "Automatic dependency installation via Ansible",
    "YARA rule support for custom detection across the entire attack surface",
    "Docker support for containerized scanning",
    "Flexible target types: domains, IPs, CIDR ranges, URLs, emails, GitHub orgs, and mobile apps"
  ],
  "publicApiSurface": [
